// === class-D HARD scale-out batch2 — rt_net_zero + rt_posix_ok + rt_net_fail
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// Batch1 (PRs #1914 + #1923 + #1929) landed rt_isalpha + rt_isalnum +
// rt_pthread_noop + rt_pthread_create_policy. This batch2 wave extends
// class-D HARD coverage with 3 more 0-arg HexaVal-repr struct-return bodies:
